snippet.title: Robert Downey Jr Defends Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard...!?
snippet.description:
Robert Downey Jr Defends Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard...!?
The case of Johnny Depp is one that is not just ongoing but seems to keep shifting. To the extent that many major stars are now backing him up ,which includes Robert Downey Jr., who has come out to speak out for Depp. We’ll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at how Robert Downey Jr. has backed Johnny Depp in his own way, and who else has sided with Depp in the matter against Amber Heard. Where do you stand on how things have gone down? Do you believe that Depp deserves this support? Or do you think that these celebs are misguided? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we’ll see you next time on the channel!
